# Copy value from cell 0 to cell 1
# Brainfuck equivalent: [->+<]

# First, put some value in cell 0 (let's say 5)
MR. THEISS!!!!! (put 5 in cell 0)

# Move to cell 1
Mr. Theiss

# Now copy from cell 0 to cell 1
Professor Theiss
  mr. theiss...    # decrement cell 0
  Mr Theiss        # move to cell 1
  MR. THEISS!      # increment cell 1
  Mr. Theiss       # move back to cell 0
Student Theiss

# Output both cells
Mr Theiss Mister Theiss? Mr. Theiss Mister Theiss?
